<br>
My point is precisely that I'm not infringing upon other people's fun.  <br>
<br>
&quot;I sent my letters. I am my own voice. I won't let your fun infringe on mine. However, if it continues to do escalate like this, infringing on the &quot;fun&quot; of some to satisfy the &quot;fun&quot; of the ubers, well, then I will take my fun elsewhere and you can have all the &quot;fun&quot; you want.&quot;<br>
<br>
Your argument seems to be &quot;non-ubers are better than ubers because ubers think they're better than non-ubers&quot;.  Which is flawed because a) the &quot;ubers&quot; of which you speak don't think they're better than anyone, and b) even if they did the premise of your argument would invalidate itself.<br>
<br>
&quot;Let me give you a clue there. We (the not so uber) get pissed when a place we want to go and have done as much due dilligence as possible to make sure no one else is planning to go there is trampled on by the &quot;ubers&quot; out for a day of &quot;fun&quot;. &quot;<br>
<br>
Why do you have more right to a particular zone or area than anyone else does?  When myself and my associates have a contested area/zone/camp/whatever, we talk to the other party and work out an arrangement.<br>
<br>
&quot;This will increase with the transfers. Yes, it is just competition and why should any consideration be given to anyone &quot;less&quot; than you.&quot;&quot;<br>
<br>
When have I shown any indication that I would behave in such way?  You're asserting that me and my friends act a certain way without any justification that we actually do.  What makes you think we follow the philosophy &quot;why should I give any consideration to those less than me?&quot; ?  What makes you think I think anyone is less than me?<br>
<br>
Start justifying your claims.<br>
<br>
&quot;I'm done. I wrote my completely ineffectual letters to SOE which are answered solely by form letter. The full brunt of my ire is directed at SOE. I am merely irritated at the attitudes of the &quot;ubers&quot; here who think anything that benefits them is good and screw how anyone else feels. I rather expect it from them. I guess I expect it from SOE, too, they couldn't care less either. &quot;<br>
<br>
Start reading and stop making assumptions.  I'm claiming that we can mutually enjoy this game.  After all I've been doing it for over a year and a half. <p>Witherweaver Wyntari<!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->65 Wizard of <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.fireandfury.org">Fire and Fury</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=113163">Witherweaver Wyntari's Profile</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kurley>Kurley</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 819<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/19/03 8:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3496.topic&index=183>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Antoin decides to dive into the fecal pile of a thread</span><hr size=1> It is my hope that at some point in this thread, Witherweaver will respond three times in a row. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=thraallfv>ThraallFV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 654<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/19/03 8:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3496.topic&index=184>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.calpoly.edu/~msamuel/frgSthrl.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Antoin decides to dive into the fecal pile of a thread</span><hr size=1> haha kurley i do hope he can then it would be a true WW.<br>
