<br>
Real fucked up view. Lets define some things before we go any further. Let me put a disclaimer before you nitpick me to death. These are my opinions. Agree or disagree with them at your leasure. These are Ideas I formed from just being on the server, and when I started here I was VERY RP Nazi, then I kinda saw how screwed up it was and I lightened up a bit.<br>
<br>
Roleplayer - Anyone who takes up a role fitting whatever game they are playing. Example? Lets make it easy, a Warrior of Rallos Zek who enjoys to fight and kill. Or on the flip side of the coin, a Warrior of Rallos Zek who feels his god is overbearing him with fighting and wishes to make admends for such. And other various ways that this 'Warrior of Rallos Zek' can be taken. No one way is wrong. No one way makes anyone a Non Roleplayer.<br>
<br>
'Ubers' - People who are well, Uber. High End conent, probably left to just be the top end guild on a server, and maybe 3-5 under guilds that are close.<br>
<br>
'Non Ubers' - Everyone else.<br>
<br>
'Non Roleplayer' - One who does not roleplay. How do you not roleplay even at the basic level is done by clearly stating that you are not a roleplayer. <br>
<br>
'Anti Roleplayer' - One who activitly engages in mocking, harrassment, annoyance, training, etc etc of one just because he roleplays. Also one who deters a Roleplayers ability to roleplay by various methods.<br>
<br>
'RP Nazi' - Roleplay Nazi's are like Anti Non Roleplayers. They do all they can, just like an Anti Roleplayer would against a roleplayer, because they don't roleplay. (Or in the RP Nazi's mind, RP 'correctly', which is an Oxymoron in itself, because if you RP, then you are RPing correctly, as long as you stay within the limits of the game. No Lazer guns and Spaceships in a Midevil game.)<br>
<br>
Now, no where does it say that Ubers can't be Roleplayers. Nor does it say Non Roleplayers trample over Roleplayers ability to RP. So stop assuming such. Thanks.<br>
<br>
Transfers. Now I'm pretty sure I can say for most RPers, we Know what our time on the other servers was like.<br>
Having our ability to play this game and enjoy it as we wanted to because some of us acually believed the Box when it said Everquest was a Multi Player Online Roleplaying Game. Most of the EQ  player base may not have, but we sure as hell did. Hook line and sinker. <br>
<br>
Just ask around on these boards, and you will find out how fucked up we were treated. It made most of us, Myself included, Quit the game. Not saying its a proper way to express yourself, but it even caused Depression in some roleplayers because of how everyone on the other servers seemed to just destroy every chance their was to RP.<br>
<br>
How many of you remember GM events that would try to advance the storyline (Abit how poorly it was done, but that's hardly the point) onyl to have a bunch of cocksucking bitches come and runin it hoping to get some 'phat lewtz' from the storytelling MOB?  Just one example of many on how RPing got shafted so hard in this game by the player base. People always say..<br>
<br>
&quot;EQ is a poor base for RPing&quot;. Even RPers say it, like Banegrivm and shit.<br>
<br>
Well, I said it once, Rules don't make RPing, people make RPing.<br>
<br>
Know what? Before May 8th, their were people that didn't Roleplay. I'm not going to name them here, you know who they were. The Rules didn't make them RP.<br>
<br>
No matter what restrictions or how good your 'Base' for RPing is, If the people don't RP. It will fail.<br>
<br>
I don't blame the game for the failure of RP on the other servers, I blame the people. They fucked it up, not Sony or Verant. Thats why the other servers are so Anti Roleplay.<br>
<br>
So, what does any of this have to do with FV? Well, its my personal opinion that FV was created for people who Perfer to Roleplay their characters, as opposed to not RPing them in this game. Bend the 'Roleplaying Preffered' tag all you want. I know I'm right. This is still our house. We just let you stay here. <br>
<br>
So when you say &quot;I don't bother the RPers and I don't hamper the RPers ability to roleplay&quot; I wonder..<br>
<br>
What the fuck do you want? A cookie? You're SUPPUSED to respect us and not hinder our ability to roleplay. Its the least you can do, for you aren't roleplaying on a server created for roleplayers. By that same token, I thank you for doing such, and not being 'Anti Roleplay'. Espically those that make the extra effort and RP a bit with us. *I* for one appricate that. <br>
<br>
I came here to get away from the Anti RP. I quit playing my old Shintou for about 2 months before I was just happening to cruse our old forms to see Jaxy's post about a RPing server comming up. I zoomed over here and all was well. When I found that their were going to be people that didn't Roleplay.. well.<br>
<br>
I was just like Why in the fuck are you following US to bother us somemore. I was very Anti Non Roleplayer, if you remember. Hell, I'm the RP Nazi after all.<br>
<br>
But throught the arguments I saw the fact that its very I guess, mean of us to come down on the Non Roleplayers. In fact, we're being just like the very people we escaped from when we came to FV. Those fuckin assholes back on the other servers. Sweeping Generalization yes. I don't care, for you really don't understand how it was back then, just like I don't understand how its so hard to raid the Planes of Power on this server.<br>
<br>
Anyhow, it all goes well. The Non Roleplayers dont hinder our RP, we let them stay without anymore arguments and it all works well. In fact, I think its made me a better Roleplayer to deal with them, to write in even Non Roleplayers into my RP so that my RP doesn't get hindered just by the simple fact that they do not roleplay. Its fun. <br>
<br>
But you see, now to the point. The Transfers. What I guess the Non Roleplayers are not understanding is what type of people their are on those other servers.<br>
<br>
Before you open your mouth and scream 'sweeping generalization', again. You don't understand. You're misinformed. Sure. Fire and Furies one little cleric guy or whatthehell ever they have comming over here can be the nicest non roleplayer in the world. I really don't care if they come over, just as long as they don't interfear with what I'm doing, which is Roleplaying.<br>
<br>
Its the fucks that *I* (and I'm sure almost every other Roleplayer that came here from another server remembers) remember who were getting in the way of my Roleplay, who were mocking and just generally stomping on *MY* fun. What the Non Roleplayers seem to fail to understand is that Everquest, hell, the WORLD isn't happy go lucky. Just like its a sweeping generalization for me to say that Everyones Mean and fucked up, its the same sweeping Generalization to say that everyone that transfers here will join FnF and will be nice to the RPing community.<br>
<br>
Wake up. This isn't Barneys Happy go lucky world. This is Everquest. This is the Internet. People are assholes, and I lost my faith in their 'Kindness' a long time ago. So If I'm going to have to shut our your little happy Non Roleplayer friends to keep the anti roleplayers off the server that was created so that we can have the freedom to roleplay, I'm sorry but that door is getting slammed, I'm gonna bolt it down and meld the damn thing shut. If your friends really want to come and play with you guys, they can create a level 1 character here, and you can PL them to death.<br>
<br>
I mean you got to high levels even before the May 8th patch in a short amount of time. Let them do the same.<br>
Again, you need to realize. This is <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>OUR</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> house. Created for us. Not for you. The only reason the Non Roleplayers really don't get flogged down is because you respect our right to roleplay in OUR house. By respecting our rights to roleplay, we respect your rights to be in OUR house. Like Shadow said.<br>
<br>
I wish this server was 100% Roleplay. But its not. At least you respect our will to RP.<br>
<br>
And if you think I'm bullshitting you, disrespect our wish to RP and see what happens. No matter how high up you may think you are,  this is still our house, you need to remember that. And at the very least, *I*'m not going to Tolerate Anti Roleplayers Transfering over to here.<br>
<br>
Sure. The Anti Roleplayers can make level 1 Characters and they probably have. But its Harder for them to find groups, even, harder so due to lack of server population because of the fact that they disrespect us in our own house. So we can keep a lid on them for the most part. Most of the Low to Midrange guilds Roleplay, and expect their members at the very least to show respect to the Owners of the House, which are the Roleplayers. Don't and you won't be guilded. And the Anti Roleplayers, Unlike the Nice Non Roleplayers that has friends in the Higher up guilds, dont have anyone to PL them.<br>
<br>
So for the most part, their best bet is the Transfer overhere Naked and do whatever.<br>
<br>
Fuck that. I'm closing the door on their asses even before they step in the door.<br>
<br>
Sorry for your nice Non Roleplayer friends, but thats the way it is, and thats the only way we can keep this house which was built for US, OURS, now and for as long as EQ goes on.<br>
<br>
This is OUR house. Remember that.<br>
Disrespect our will to Roleplay at your OWN risk, that being your ability to enjoy your time here on FV.<br>
<br>
That is all.<br>
Have a nice day. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Shintou.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kaileena>Kaileena</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_whitespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Evil never looked so good.<br>New Mod!</span><br>  Posts: 862<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/20/03 7:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3496.topic&index=200>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.studioeternity.com/blessed/images/Kaidoll.gif width=65 height=114></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: This Horse is too strong to die. It'sa Purebred Stallion</span><hr size=1> Eek, I tried to stay away from this thread.. but as Mod.. I guess it's like.. kinda my job now or whatever.<br>
